text: Stig Lindewall (born 15 August 1936) is a Swedish gymnast. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Sweden Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
